commit_message: JAMS runs from any directory after adding script dir to path
Merge branch 'main' of https://github.com/csglab/JAMS into main
check arguments (files exist, ints are ints etc), use out_dir and experiment id for predict
prompt error if provided task is not a real one, fix demo files: used GLM instead of BUILD
add reproducible JAMS script for TFs in the manuscript
add license GNU General Public License v3.0
improve doc for predict task, cap predict heatmap cases to 1000, if more then sample 1000
Improved README.md, and added demo data
adding PREDICT task, and --motif_in_regions option, where it can search best motif match or use the start of a bed file to predict binding
